               <p>Ann Christian I happened to be in the Yard, and heard my Mistress scream out; I found her in the Passage, upon the Ground, and the Prisoner lying upon her; he knocked me down, and stunn'd me, and knock'd the Candlestick out of my Hand; he owned the Fact before the Justice, and said, that he did intend to rob them that Night.</p>
